hy sMq jno! pRBU Awp hI Awpxw Awp (iksy jIv dy ihrdy ivc) prgt krdw hY, auh Al`K hY, aus dw shI srUp ibAwn nhIN kIqw jw skdw ]6]
(hy sMq jno! jIvW nUM) Awqmk mOq dy ky (iPr) Awp hI pRBU Awqmk jIvn dyNdw hY[ aus nUM iksy qrHW dw koeI rqw Br BI lwlc nhIN hY ]7]
hy sMq jno! jgq ivc prmwqmw ny keI jIvW nUM dUijAW dI mdd krn dy smr`Q bxw idqw hY, keI jIv aus ny kMgwl-mMgqy bxw idqy hn[ (ijn@W auqy imhr krdw hY auhnW pwsoN) AwpxI BgqI prmwqmw Awp hI krWdw hY ]8]
hy sMq jno! ijn@W bMidAW ny iek prmwqmw nwl jwx-pCwx bxw leI hY auh v`fy BwgW vwly hn, auh sdw kwiem rihx vwly pRBU (dI Xwd) ivc lIn rihMdy hn ]9]
