hy sMq jno! hryk jIv dy AMdr prmwqmw Awp hI duK pYdw krdw hY[ Awp hI suK (BI) dyNdw hY[ auh Awp hI jIv nUM Btkxw ivc pw ky aus nUM kurwhy pw dyNdw hY ]11]
hy sMq jno! ijs mnuK ny gurU dI srn leI, aus ny aus v`fy dwqwr pRBU nwl sWJ pw leI; pr mwieAw dy moh ivc AMnHI hoeI lokweI BtkdI iPrdI hY ]12]
hy sMq jno! ijn@W nUM gurU ny (nwm AMimRq dI) kdr b^SI, ijn@W ny (ies qrHW nwm-AMimRq) cK ilAw, auhnW nUM aus dw AwnMd Aw igAw (qy auh sdw nwm ivc juVy rhy) ]13]
(hy sMq jno! jIvW dy v`s dI g`l nhIN) keI jIvW nUM prmwqmw Awp (hI) Awpxy nwm qoN KuMJw dyNdw hY, qy keI jIvW nUM gurU dI srn pw ky (Awpxy nwm dI) sUJ b^S dyNdw hY ]14]
hy sMq jno! aus prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh sdw krdy irhw kro sdw krdy irhw kro[ aus (pRBU) dw nwmxw bhuq v`fw hY ]15]
hy sMq jno! pRBU qoN ibnw (aus dy brwbr dw) hor koeI pwiqSwh nhIN hY[ aus ny pUrw iensw& kr ky is&q-swlwh krn dI ieh rIq clweI hY ]16]
hy sMq jno! aus prmwqmw dw hI iensw& (krn vwlw hukm) sdw At`l hY, iksy ivrly (BwgW vwly) nUM auh pRBU (ieh) hukm mMnx leI pRyrnw krdw hY ]17]
hy pRwxie! ijs prmwqmw ny (bMidAW vwsqy) gurU dy snmuK rihx dI mrXwdw clweI hoeI hY, sdw aus dw iDAwn Drdy irhw kro ]18]
hy sMq jno! (ijhVw mnu`K) gurU nUM imldw hY (Bwv, gurU dI srn pYNdw hY), ijs mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc (gurU, prmwqmw dw) nwm vsWdw hY auh mnu`K (izMdgI dI Kyf ivc) kwmXwb ho jWdw hY ]19]
hy sMq jno! (gurU AwpxI) bwxI dI rwhIN (Awpxy) Sbd dI rwhIN (srn Awey is`KW nUM ieh aupdyS) suxWdw rihMdw hY ik prmwqmw sdw kwiem rihx vwlw hY prmwqmw sdw kwiem rihx vwlw hY ]20]
hy nwnk! (hy sMq jno!) prmwqmw Ascrj-rUp hY, myrw prmwqmw sBnIN QweIN mOjUd hY (hryk jIv ivAwpk ho ky) auh (hryk dy idl dI) sux irhw hY, (hryk dw kMm) vyK irhw hY ]21]5]14]
